<item>
            <title>[LU-4490] Test failure conf-sanity test_69: createmany gets &quot;File too large&quot;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4490</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Nathaniel Clark &amp;lt;nathaniel.l.clark@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/db93e86e-7ddb-11e3-908b-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/db93e86e-7ddb-11e3-908b-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Previous runs that timed out because createmany didn&apos;t fail nicely:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/64fa24c4-7d4b-11e3-8d29-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/64fa24c4-7d4b-11e3-8d29-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/e3e822a0-7d4a-11e3-8d29-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/e3e822a0-7d4a-11e3-8d29-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/66dbcd2e-7a67-11e3-86c8-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/66dbcd2e-7a67-11e3-86c8-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_69 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;createmany: failed to create 100000 files: 27&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: conf-sanity 69&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test log&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;CMD: wtm-11vm7 lctl list_param osc.lustre-OST*-osc             &amp;gt; /dev/null 2&amp;gt;&amp;amp;1
CMD: wtm-11vm7 lctl get_param -n osc.lustre-OST0000-osc-MDT0000.prealloc_last_id
 - created 10000 (time 1389720773.72 total 53.92 last 53.92)
 - created 20000 (time 1389720826.72 total 106.92 last 53.00)
 - created 30000 (time 1389720881.25 total 161.45 last 54.53)
 - created 40000 (time 1389720935.65 total 215.86 last 54.41)
open(/mnt/lustre/d69.conf-sanity/f69.conf-sanity-49786) error: File too large
total: 49786 creates in 271.07 seconds: 183.66 creates/second
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;New &quot;faster&quot; fail is due to &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/8841&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/8841&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
